{"tid":2415813,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓索網紅獲1400萬打賞 由驚訝到爆喊引熱議","createTime":"2021-02-20T14:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T23:26:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":70,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fffbb43bf8a3a0848f071e87235e825f3f1fd5","tid":2415813,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_S1BeBnWSC9tXEzJ8ITu99aoKjY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MDK6KOJERZA4HB3TDJWKBXRGNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_S1BeBnWSC9tXEzJ8ITu99aoKjY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMDK6KOJERZA4HB3TDJWKBXRGNU.jpg&h=bc58821b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國近年不少網紅都活躍於YouTube及做直播主吸金，當中在韓國網站AfreecaTV更有不少直播主、BJ人氣爆燈，他們靠網上直播大搵真銀。近日一名美女BJ安可（音譯）在直播途中獲得價值20億韓圜（約1,410萬港元）的2千萬個氣球打賞，當中她直播時的表情由驚訝到失落，因而成為網民熱烈的討論對象。<br />\n<br />\n如中六合彩<br />\nBJ安可日前做直播時，突然有一名fans向她送了2,055萬4,432個氣球打賞，由於氣球數量換算成現金的話，總值超過20億韓圜的鉅額，所以即時讓所有網民大吃一驚。而BJ安可自己看到氣球數量後，似乎都難以置信地睜大了眼睛，表示驚訝，並好久都未能說出話來，驚慌得眨了眨眼睛，十足十中了六合彩一樣。不過其後AfreecaTV方面作出更正，指是數量顯示的錯誤，令BJ安可即時失落得流下眼淚來。最後BJ安可更哭着說：「真煩人。」但還是為了其他觀眾於直播中認真跳舞，吸引了網民的視線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/83okA8RooKcA65fNBgQMPJ06A4s=/802x447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ROSWGTQVLZFN7DFJIB3HQKUADE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F83okA8RooKcA65fNBgQMPJ06A4s%3D%2F802x447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FROSWGTQVLZFN7DFJIB3HQKUADE.png&h=943a2ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nAkoYrelfnxIDmaef9JlgxI3WP0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UL72UR6QTBCGFMJVHTB6N73K64.jpg\" da