，似乎都難以置信地睜大了眼睛，表示驚訝，並好久都未能說出話來，驚慌得眨了眨眼睛，十足十中了六合彩一樣。不過其後AfreecaTV方面作出更正，指是數量顯示的錯誤，令BJ安可即時失落得流下眼淚來。最後BJ安可更哭着說：「真煩人。」但還是為了其他觀眾於直播中認真跳舞，吸引了網民的視線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/83okA8RooKcA65fNBgQMPJ06A4s=/802x447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ROSWGTQVLZFN7DFJIB3HQKUADE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F83okA8RooKcA65fNBgQMPJ06A4s%3D%2F802x447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FROSWGTQVLZFN7DFJIB3HQKUADE.png&h=943a2ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nAkoYrelfnxIDmaef9JlgxI3WP0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UL72UR6QTBCGFMJVHTB6N73K64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnAkoYrelfnxIDmaef9JlgxI3WP0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUL72UR6QTBCGFMJVHTB6N73K64.jpg&h=2ab59b59&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"事實好明顯係真係有有錢仔課左咁多，不過個platform 食曬，再話係bug. 賭場都成日用lee 招，server 收到幾多錢做自動計，好簡單既加減，點會有機會錯？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"咁個有錢仔有睇直播會唔知比人食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b8cb2723b0b030d05e624b468746a375f53b21","tid":2415813,"uid":206200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1c35fc00c6a6bf880c1c635423d75503ac1e14c","tid":2415813,"uid":80679,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會比個平台食夾棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"一定會食架啦，唔係d平台賺咩？"},{"pid":"95d60266be5530f32689e38c80ea83485151465b","tid":2415813,"uid":714